data.description: Just one year old home! Welcome to The Camelia plan by Centex Homes features a two-story home with an open and inviting gathering area. A gourmet kitchen with an oversized pantry and island with an eat-in bar top lends extra dining space. The spacious upstairs loft offers an entertaining retreat for game time and movie nights! Many features include modern cabinets, granite countertops, stainless cabinet hardware, upgraded flooring throughout, full gutters, a sprinkler system, and MUCH MORE. Zoned to Katy ISD. Sunterra Community features a 3.5-acre Crystal Blue Lagoon with white sand beaches, palm trees, cabanas, watercraft rentals of kayaks, paddleboards, etc! Clubhouse, event center, swim-up beach bar, swimming pool, and splash pad – resort- style living at its finest. Come and see this beautiful home!
